            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299757</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="" data-start="79" data-end="326">Samsung 与国际级艺术盛事 Art Basel 展开全球合作，成为今年四地展会（包括香港、瑞士巴塞尔、巴黎及美国迈阿密海滩）的官方艺术展示电视品牌。这次联乘也见证 Samsung 推出「2025 全新 Art TV 系列」的全球首展。今日 Samsung 率先于香港会议展览中心亮相的 ArtCube 展区，由升级版画框电视 The Frame Pro、Micro LED、Neo QLED 8K 及 QLED 构建沉浸式艺术空间，展现如何透过创新技术，让艺术走入日常生活。</p><p class="" data-start="328" data-end="448">Samsung 香港区董事总经理赵依音表示，今次合作有助推动当代艺术普及化，亦让品牌与 Art Basel 的国际艺廊与艺术家建立长远伙伴关系。「2025 全新 Art TV 系列」希望将艺术欣赏体验由展场延伸至家中，打破地域与形式的限制。</p><p data-start="328" data-end="448"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151958_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299768 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151958_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151958_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151958_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 data-start="450" data-end="480">Samsung Art Store 推动全球艺术串流平台</h2><p class="" data-start="482" data-end="678">Samsung 除了以最新电视硬件提升视觉效果，亦积极透过 Samsung Art Store 将世界级艺术带进千家万户。由即日起，用户可以在 Art TV 系列的画面上，串流欣赏来自 Art Basel 香港展会精选的 23 幅艺廊作品。这些作品将于 3 月 26 日至 30 日期间于会展现场展出，同时也能透过 Art Store 以 4K 解像度在家观赏，感受艺术原作的色彩层次与细节。</p><p data-start="482" data-end="678"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299762" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p data-start="482" data-end="678"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299763" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="" data-start="680" data-end="833">Samsung 自 2017 年推出 The Frame 画框电视后，至今已与超过 70 间国际博物馆及艺廊，包括 MoMA、罗浮宫及梵高博物馆合作，累积超过 3,000 件艺术作品供订阅欣赏。今年起，这些艺术资源将支援 MICRO LED、Neo QLED 及 QLED 系列电视，扩展至更广泛用户层面。</p><p data-start="680" data-end="833"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungartstore.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299764" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungartstore-694x382.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="382" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungartstore-694x382.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungartstore.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p data-start="680" data-end="833"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/artistmarcdennis.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299765" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/artistmarcdennis-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/artistmarcdennis-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/artistmarcdennis.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 data-start="835" data-end="855">ArtCube 展区带来互动艺术体验</h2><p class="" data-start="857" data-end="1085">今年 Art Basel 香港展会新增名为「ArtCube」的互动展区，选址于香港会议展览中心 L3 层大堂。展览主题为「Borderless, Dive into the Art」，由五位国际艺术家（Lee Kunyong、Aerosyn-Lex Mestrovic、Saya Woolfalk、Marc Dennis 及 Jules de Balincount）联同参展艺廊携手策展，观众可透过 2025 年系列电视沉浸式体验结合科技与艺术的创作魅力。</p><p class="" data-start="1087" data-end="1105">ArtCube 于以下时间对外开放：</p><ul data-start="1106" data-end="1193"><li class="" data-start="1106" data-end="1134"><p class="" data-start="1108" data-end="1134">3 月 28 日（星期五）下午 2 时至晚上 8 时</p></li><li class="" data-start="1135" data-end="1163"><p class="" data-start="1137" data-end="1163">3 月 29 日（星期六）下午 2 时至晚上 8 时</p></li><li class="" data-start="1164" data-end="1193"><p class="" data-start="1166" data-end="1193">3 月 30 日（星期日）中午 12 时至下午 6 时</p></li></ul><h2 data-start="1195" data-end="1226"></h2><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152712_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299772 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152712_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152712_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152712_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/yiyinzhaomanagingdir.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/yiyinzhaomanagingdir-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/yiyinzhaomanagingdir-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/yiyinzhaomanagingdir.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152113_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299770 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152113_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152113_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152113_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152020_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152020_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152020_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152020_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151956_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151956_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151956_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151956_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151953_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299776" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151953_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151953_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151953_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 data-start="1195" data-end="1226">The Frame Pro 首度亮相，无线连接扩展家居美学</h2><p class="" data-start="1228" data-end="1374">全新 The Frame Pro 画框电视于今次展会首次公开亮相，推出支援 4K 144Hz 无线影音传输的 Wireless One Connect 技术，有效传输范围达 10 米，摆放方式更灵活，打破传统空间限制。画质方面，升级至 Neo QLED 显示技术，还原艺术作品真实色彩与细节。</p><p data-start="1228" data-end="1374"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05405.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05405-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05405-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05405.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p data-start="1228" data-end="1374"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05409.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299777" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05409-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05409-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05409.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p data-start="1228" data-end="1374"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05410.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05410-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05410-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05410.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p data-start="1228" data-end="1374"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05411.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299779" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05411-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05411-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05411.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="" data-start="1376" data-end="1516">除了硬件提升，The Frame Pro 每月提供超过 370 件免费艺术品串流，并内置 Samsung Art Store，收藏全球著名艺术馆如 MoMA、罗浮宫的作品，亦独家加入 Art Basel 精选艺术品。该系列亦获得色彩权威机构 PANTONE 认证，保证画面还原度。</p><p class="" data-start="1518" data-end="1604">香港 Samsung 网上商店现正接受预订，凡于 3 月 27 日至 4 月 13 日期间订购，将获一年 Art Store 免费订阅及电视边框一套（数量有限，先到先得）。</p><p data-start="1518" data-end="1604"><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/samsung-art-basel/wireless-home/audio-visual/">Samsung 联乘 Art Basel 引领艺术新视界，展示全新「The Frame Pro」艺术电视系列</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
