            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299618</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日下午，小米旗下的子品牌 POCO 就在新加坡发布了新一代的旗舰机款 F7 系列，当中除了预期之内的 F7 Pro 外，还首次推出旗下首部 Ultra 机款：POCO F7 Ultra。现在就让 Edward 带大家到现场，看看这两部手机有甚么特别吧。</p><h2>POCO F7 系列 = Redmi K80 系列变奏版</h2><p>今次 POCO 发布的两部全新 F7 系列手机，分别是 F7 Pro 及 F7 Ultra，其实他们本身就是去年小米在中国发布的 Redmi K80 及 K80 Pro 的变奏版，所以大体设计上及规格上都十分相似。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02624-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02624-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02624.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>F7 Ultra 首次引入长焦镜</h2><p>先说今次两部新机较高阶的一部：POCO F7 Ultra，它属于旗舰级数机款，配备了最新 Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Elite 处理器、12GB / 16GB LPDDR5X RAM 及 256GB / 512GB UFS 4.1 内存，亦内建了 6.67 吋 2K 解析度 120Hz 更新率 Flow AMOLED 荧幕，所以整体配置上均与现时市场上的旗舰手机分别不大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02630-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02630-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02630.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299713" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02471-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02471-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02471.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02472-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02472-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02472.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而它既然说得上 Ultra，自然拥有最强硬件，最明显就是强化了相机配置，除了内建采用 Light Fusion 800 感光元件的 5,000 万像素主摄镜及拥有 120 度 FOV 的 3,200 万像素超广角镜外，更首次将长焦镜引入到 POCO 旗舰机上，而且规格亦达到 5,000 万像素 2.5x 光学变焦，令 POCO F7 Ultra 不只打机上表现理想，相机成像亦可与市场上的旗舰手机媲美，使用家终于可以「鱼与熊掌兼得」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02641-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02641-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02641.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299716" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02652-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02652-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02652.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02561-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02561-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02561.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>散热方面，POCO F7 Ultra 依然内建了 LiquidCool 4.0 技术，它内建了立体双通道 IceLoop 散热系统及大达 5400mm² 超大导热管，令硬件可进一步下降 3 度。加上它首次内建了 WildBoost Optimization 4.0 技术，利用 AI 自动按需要调节硬件需求，令用家即使玩对图像处理要求较高的游戏时，依然有十分理想的效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02378-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02378-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02378.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02483-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02483-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02483.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>官方表示有了这项技术后，触控反应可有 12% 的提升，而追踪反应亦可最多提升 22%。官方更表示即使以 2K 120fps 设定运作如《原神》这类游戏，亦可长时间维持在高水平的帧率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02732-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02732-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02732.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02752-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02752-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02752.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>至于电量方面，POCO F7 Ultra 亦内建了 5,300mAh 容量电池，足够用家用上一日以上，它亦支援 120W 有线快充及 50W 无线快充，即使回电亦十分快。当然，它亦支援 IP68 防水防尘功能，令用家使用上更加安心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02589-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02589-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02589.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
